The COMPLETE, VERBATIM text of the GNU Affero General Public License, Version 3,
must be inserted below this notice before this repository is published. The full
text was not embedded automatically because the environment that prepared this
change had no network access, and a license document must be byte-exact rather
than hand-transcribed. To complete it, run (with network):

    ./scripts/fetch-license.sh
    # equivalently:
    curl -fsSL https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt -o LICENSE

The canonical machine-readable identifier for this project is:

    SPDX-License-Identifier: AGPL-3.0-or-later

(also declared in package.json). Verify the fetched text against
<https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt> during the legal review.
